<!--Before putting The Right Honourable in front of his name please read [[Wikipedia:Manual of Style (biographies)#Honorific prefixes]] -->I '''Stephen Joseph Harper''' {{Post-nominals|post-noms=[[Queen's Privy Council for Canada|PC]] [[Member of the Canadian House of Commons|MP]]}} (mibait Abril 30, 1959) ing [[Listahan da reng Pun Ministru ning Canada|kadwang pulu't adwa]] ampong [[Pun Ministru ning Canada|Pun Ministru]] ning [[Canada]] ampo ing pekapun ning [[Conservative Party of Canada|Conservative Party]]. Megi yang pun ministru i Harper anyang mibalangkas yang  [[kapamahalang minorya]] (''minority government'') kaybat ning [[alalang pederal ning Canada, 2006|alalang pederal ning 2006]]. Ya ing mumunang pun ministru ibat king mibayung Conservative Party, kaybat ning pamisanib da reng partidung [[Progressive Conservative Party of Canada|Progressive Conservative]] ampong [[Canadian Alliance]].

